name: paste
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "paste" %}
{% set version = "2.0.3" %}
{% set build = 0 %}

package:
  name: {{ name }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://bitbucket.org/ianb/paste/get/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: d6b1ac1223c42d0a8de5e5fa46b142bff688d4f535738a0ba938d9b0a78533dd

build:
  number: {{ build }}
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - six >=1.4.0

  run:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - six >=1.4.0

test:
  imports:
    - paste
    - paste.auth
    - paste.cowbell
    - paste.debug
    - paste.evalexception
    - paste.exceptions
    - paste.util
  requires:
    - nose >=0.11

about:
  home: http://pythonpaste.org
  license: MIT
  summary: 'Tools for using a Web Server Gateway Interface stack'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - kwilcox
    - daf

about.summary: Tools for using a Web Server Gateway Interface stack
